This Snapshot Released On Sunday April 5 2026

1 Added GRUB Background

For Existing Triaxis Users

Open terminal Then sudo nano /etc/default/grub
The Uncomment # On GRUB_BACKGROUND"/path/to/wallpaper"
Then Change GRUB_BACKGROUND"/path/to/wallpaper" To GRUB_BACKGROUND"/usr/share/wallpapers/Frozenworld Or Frozenworld Compile IT"
Example GRUB_BACKGROUND"GRUB_BACKGROUND"/usr/share/wallpapers/Frozenworld-Compile-It/Frozenworld (Compile It).png"

2 TUR Has Been Discontinued On Sunday April 5 2026 And Moved To https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux-Archive Since Its Now Useless RIP TUR Saturday January 10 2026-Sunday April 5 2026

3 Added SUPPORT URL
  For Existing Triaxis Users Run sudo nano /etc/os-release then change SUPPORT_URL="https://bbs.archlinux.org/" To SUPPORT_URL="https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux/discussions/3"
